Version 1.0beta6 – released 2017-06-24
see <https://github.com/cmb69/cryptographp_xh/milestone/2?closed=1>

Version 1.0beta5 – released 2017-03-10
see <https://github.com/cmb69/cryptographp_xh/milestone/1?closed=1>

Version 1beta4 - released 2015-01-01
* raised requirements to CMSimple_XH >= 1.6 and PHP >= 5.1.2
* fixed bug, where no audio CAPTCHA was available when language files were
  missing
* removed large and unknown licensed font files
* added version.nfo
* added metaconfig.php
* added German localization (though not for audio files) and manual

Version 1beta3 - released 2012-05-03
* updated czech translation (constributed by oldnema)
* added jplayer to stream audio CAPTCHA with graceful degradation by offering a
  file download (degrades)
* removed language code from session
* added detection of GD capabilities to system check
* corrected vertical alignment of visual CAPTCHAs

Version 1beta2 - released 2012-04-22
* fixed buggy requirement check
* extended copyright to 2012
* changed usage of original cryptographp: instead of using it as library it's
  now fully integrated
* fixed cryptographps local file inclusion bug
* implemented audio captcha
* removed config options char_case_sensitive and crypt_secure
* moved cryptographp config to config/
* added alt attributes for captcha and buttons
* added plugin icon
* allowed multiple idependent instances (removed crypt_use_max and
  crypt_one_use)
* integrated error.php to cryptographp.php
* added warning, if cookies are disabled
* made crypt_use_timer_error a boolean config option
* updated the manual
* moved the updating of the configuration to index.php
* implemented expiration of CAPTCHAs
* added slovak translation (provided by Tata)
* added czech translation (provided by oldnema)
* made several minor improvements

Version 1beta1 - released 2011-09-19
* initial release
